OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1772547086
OL,3,CHarry Styles' 'One Night Only in
OL,4,CManchester' will be phone-free
OL,6,FHarry Styles has confirmed that his
OL,7,Fhighly anticipated "One Night Only"
OL,8,Fperformance will be phone-free - but
OL,9,Ffans will still be able to stream the
OL,10,Fgig
OL,12,FThe 32-year-old global superstar
OL,13,FStyles announced last month that he
OL,14,Fwill perform his brand new album, Kiss
OL,15,FAll the Time. Disco, Occasionally, at
OL,16,FManchester's Co-Op Live Arena on
OL,17,FFriday, 6 March, with tickets costing
OL,18,F#20.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
