OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1772547086
OL,3,CHarry Styles' 'One Night Only in
OL,4,CManchester' will be phone-free
OL,6,FNow, it has been announced that the
OL,7,Fevent will be recorded and available
OL,8,Fto watch for subscribers of Netflix
OL,10,FTitled "Harry Styles. One Night in
OL,11,FManchester," the film will be released
OL,12,Ftwo days after Styles takes to the
OL,13,Fstage on Sunday, 8 March.
OL,15,FThe special concert comes just days
OL,16,Fafter he opened the BRIT Awards at the
OL,17,Fsame venue with his new chart-topping
OL,18,Fsingle 'Aperture'.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
