CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1772547086
OL,3,CHarry Styles' 'One Night Only in
OL,4,CManchester' will be phone-free
OL,6,FFans attending the "One Night Only"
OL,7,Fgig will be required to lock their
OL,8,Fphones away and given a disposable
OL,9,Fcamera, meaning the crowd can still
OL,10,Fcapture the memories and share them
OL,11,Fafterwards.
OL,13,FSupporters will still have access to
OL,14,Ftheir devices in case of an emergency,
OL,15,Fbut the camera function will not be
OL,16,Faccessible.
OL,18,FThis marks the first time a complete
OL,19,FHarry Styles concert performance will
OL,20,Fbe available on-demand through a major
OL,21,Fstreaming service.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
