OL,3,CHarry Styles' 'One Night Only in
OL,4,CManchester' will be phone-free
OL,6,FStyles launched his solo career after
OL,7,Fhe and fellow One Direction members
OL,8,FNiall Horan, Liam Payne and Louis
OL,9,FTomlinson went on hiatus in 2016,
OL,10,Falmost a year after Zayn Malik left
OL,11,Fthe group.
OL,13,FThe Worcestershire-born star, who grew
OL,14,Fup in Holmes Chapel, Cheshire,
OL,15,Freleased his self-titled debut solo
OL,16,Falbum in 2017, followed by Fine Line
OL,17,Fin 2019 and Harry's House in 2022.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
