OL,3,CHarry Styles' 'One Night Only in
OL,4,CManchester' will be phone-free
OL,6,FStyles has also had two UK number one
OL,7,Fsingles as a solo artist with As It
OL,8,FWas and Sign Of The Times, and won
OL,9,Fmultiple Grammy and Brit awards.
OL,11,FListen to the ITV News' entertainment
OL,12,Fpodcast, Unscripted.
